      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRETHORN (4) has been out of the placings at her last two outings but shapes well for this if she can recapture her blistering win a few runs back, getting around Grafton over 450m in 25.17. Has the ability and looks hard to top. GOLDMINE FIRE (1) stalked the lead but wound up strongly to score (41.66) at this track in Grade 5 over 710m. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and three minor placings from five starts. Sure to measure up. SOIREE (8) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 3 lengths (41.89) at The Gardens. Can measure up again. STARFIRE TEARS (2) placed last time (34.91) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten 3 lengths. Has already won three times from this draw.",
